<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A legend is a graphical object that displays the legend of a chart. The legend state is updated by <db:link xlink:href="qchart-qtcharts.xml">QChart</db:link> when series change. By default, the legend is attached to the chart, but it can be detached to make it independent of chart layout. Legend objects cannot be created or deleted, but they can be referenced via the <db:link xlink:href="qchart-qtcharts.xml">QChart</db:link> class.</db:para>
